data.description: Amazing split level beauty on a quiet street less than a mile from the Atlanta Beltline Trail.  Gorgeous one-acre corner lot with double carport, beautifully manicured front yard, stunning private backyard.  4 bedrooms, 2 full baths, plus a HUGE Bonus Room! Totally renovated new Kitchen with new cabinets and charcoal stainless-steel appliances.  New roof, new paint, new gutters, new large front and rear decks, gorgeous hardwood floors, warm fireplace, new bathrooms, lighting and hardware throughout, modern accents and architectural details everywhere!
